How to configure? Please follow this prcedure:
Step 1: Install Android SDK
- install Java SDK
- install Android Studio

Step 2: Install GO

Step 3: Install noVNC
$ sudo git clone git://github.com/kanaka/noVNC

Step 4: Git Clone NODE source code
$ git clone https://github.com/tianhongbo/node.git

Step 5: Modify source code
- install.sh
- deviceinstall.sh

1. /etc/environment
1)add emulator and node bin to PATH
/home/ubuntu/android-sdk-linux/tools
/home/ubuntu/node/bin

2)add GOPATH
$ export GOPATH=~/controller
e.g. /home/ubuntu2/controller

2. /etc/rc.local
start node automatically when instance booting
su ubuntu - -c /home/ubuntu/node/bin/node

